WEBVTT

00:15:57.840 --> 00:16:00.876
And far too many parents will be notified

00:16:00.900 --> 00:16:05.542
that their son or daughter
has died of a drug overdose.

00:16:06.454 --> 00:16:08.550
It doesn't have to be this way.

00:16:10.444 --> 00:16:11.594
Thank you.

00:16:11.618 --> 00:16:16.912
(Applause)